lead_paragraph: Fifth seed Simona Halep of Romania took advantage of an error-prone display by American Madison Keys to claim her 14th WTA title with a 7-6(2) 6-3 victory in the Rogers Cup final in Montreal on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Halep Beats Erratic Keys to Win Rogers Cup
headline.main: Halep Beats Erratic Keys to Win Rogers Cup
